  'cbc9b6d9-f525-4835-a2e0-90826a763626',
  $CORPUS$causing a postponement of a hearing will be charged a postponement fee, as set forth in the arbitration fee schedule.
24. Arbitration in the Absence of a Party or Advisor
Subject to Section XI.J., the arbitration may proceed in the absence of any party or Advisor who, after notice, fails to be present
or to obtain a postponement. The Arbitrator shall require the party who is present to submit evidence the Arbitrator may require
for an Arbitration Decision.
25. Standard of Proof
The Arbitration shall use a preponderance of the evidence standard to determine if a Participant has violated the Code.
