  '38d0db15-f019-475f-a31e-ee9894edb60e',
  $CORPUS$Organization  in  a  defined  time-limited  setting  with  the
understanding that, if an agreement for Substantial Assistance
or a case resolution agreement is not finalized, the information
provided by the Athlete or other Person in this particular setting
may not be used by the Anti-Doping Organization against the
Athlete or other Person in any Results Management proceeding
under the Code, and that the information provided by the
Anti-Doping Organization in this particular setting may not be
used by the Athlete or other Person against the Anti-Doping
Organization in any Results Management proceeding under the
Code. Such an agreement shall not preclude the Anti-Doping
Organization, Athlete or other Person from using any information
or evidence gathered from any source other than during the
specific time-limited setting described in the agreement.$CORPUS$,
