  $CORPUS$Athlete Rights & ResponsibilitiesFAQAccess To InformationEquity & DiversityVoice & RepresentationOpportunity To ParticipateSafe EnvironmentGrievance & Dispute ResolutionAthlete ResponsibilitiesMoreRelated ContentAthlete Rights & ResponsibilitiesFAQAccess To InformationEquity & DiversityVoice & RepresentationOpportunity To ParticipateSafe EnvironmentGrievance & Dispute ResolutionAthlete ResponsibilitiesAthlete Rights And ResponsibilitiesThis information is intended to simplify and support Team USA athlete education around a complex system of rights and responsibilities within the U.S. Olympic and Paralympic Movements. Learn more about your rights as a Team USA athlete by referring to the applicable laws or governance documents.If you have a specific concern or situation, please refer to the Frequently Asked Questions for guidance or reach out to any member of the network of support listed below.
 
